en_63705_0	Starting Jan. 1, the production and distribution of polythene below 20 microns will be prohibited.
en_63705_1	Chairman of the Central Environmental Authority Lal Dharmasiri said that this measure was taken after taking into account the environmental pollution caused by such polythene material.
en_63705_2	He added that around 20 million polythene material is used in the country each day.
